                  difficulty,
                  style: TextStyle(fontSize: 10, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold),
                ),
                ElevatedButton(
                  onPressed: onDeploy,
                  style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
                    backgroundColor: color,
                    minimumSize: Size(60, 28),
                  ),
                  child: Text('Deploy', style: TextStyle(fontSize: 10)),
